  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Goal:

    Utilize alotted Plays and Discards to reach the score threshold
    each shift.


    How to Play:

    - Press M to view list of Dishes you can
    make as well as bonus scoring info

    - Select Ingredients from the pantry
    and Play or Discard them.

    - Plays consist of 4 Ingredients, Discards consist
    of 1-4.

    - After clearing the score threshold, purchase Upgrades and Chefs
    in the shop. These will help you score big!


    Tips:

    - Keep and eye on
    your Plays and Discards!

    - Play the Dishes/Ingredients you have upgraded'
